'''Ubisoft Paris''' is a French video game developer founded in 1986. It's also Ubisoft's headquarters. The studio is known for the ''[[Rayman]]'', ''[[Tom Clancy's Ghost Recon]]'', ''[[Rayman#Raving Rabbids|Raving Rabbids]]'' and ''[[Just Dance (video game)|Just Dance]]'' video game series.
